This version hits differently😍 the first time I’ve listened to Asma Ul Husna the Malaysian nasyid group(Hijjaz) version in my school 18 years ago, every Friday.

Listening to this again after so many years but unique version by Atif Aslam, love the pause in between and ending tune sounds soooo magical. Still could follow the words as I remember those days. 🙏🏼👍🏻
